articles.title: MotoGP track action in India delayed by hazy 'logistics issues' - The Race
articles.description: An unusual reason is thought to be behind the "logistics issue" hold-up that affected the opening day of MotoGP action in India
articles.content:
The opening day of track action for the Indian Grand Prix has been hit by a 45-minute delay due to what has been described as a logistical issue.
